機率幫到有需要既人。咁當然你朋友唔捐比你都得，說到佢每個月捐錢都已經令到成個抗爭多左500都好呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T23:47:01.000Z","msg":"咁有咩平台基金收錢先說服到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T00:29:11.000Z","msg":"無架宜家想做既就係 你信a組織 而你身邊既人信你 咁樣去建立信任 我試過都ok ge 其實有d似保險咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6999000b46d83126ee6581c2c609b037beec795b","tid":1592511,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T00:35:02.000Z","msg":"其實我都知咁樣做唔係容易<br />\n但宜家行動既人真係唔多<br />\n如果資源係靠行動組自己捐出黎<br />\n同時大既組織先囉到被動既抗爭者既資源真係無好好利用到人多既優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊集思廣義啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e27fa30c1569cef6cee6ba32d1070f4222f1f132","tid":1592511,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6999000b46d83126ee6581c2c609b037beec795b","tid":1592511,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T00:35:02.000Z","msg":"其實我都知咁樣做唔係容易<br />\n但宜家行動既人真係唔多<br />\n如果資源係靠行動組自己捐出黎<br />\n同時大既組織先囉到被動既抗爭者既資源真係無好好利用到人多既優勢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊集思廣義啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-25T00:35:33.000Z","msg":"益"},{"pid":"5a29817cfd4e9eae3ebba55871cefbcc7df15690","tid":1592511,"uid":265195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1030893d6529cd837fd8b074f0553972646f733f","tid":1592511,"uid":292497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf1d8d262cf148b8d277ff3affa38dd8b65a1f29","tid":1592511,"uid":265195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T17:00:50.000Z","msg":"點&quot;叫&quot;和理非去每個月捐錢先<br />\n整份同意書出嚟叫佢哋簽？如果說服多一個人每月捐$500就可以問發起人一次